# System Message Rules

Correctly detect and separate:
- encryption notices
- joined group messages
- left group messages
- missed call notices
- deleted message notices
- renamed group messages

Avoid:
- treating system messages as emotional conversation

System noise should never pollute:
- most used words
- emotional pacing
- participant statistics
- report insights

---

# Encoding & Language Rules

