- multilingual chats
- mixed-language conversations
- encoding inconsistencies

Detect:
- broken character encoding
- malformed Unicode
- duplicate emoji corruption
- locale-specific export variations

Never:
- strip emotionally meaningful language accidentally

---

# Noise Reduction Rules

